{{Lunisolar March}} '''March 3''' is the 3rd day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1583]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|羽柴秀吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (later known as {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) captured {{ill|Kashida Katsuie|ja|柴田勝家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’s forces by taking {{ill|Ise Province|ja|伊勢|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’s {{ill|Kameyama Castle|ja|亀山城 (伊勢国)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in a prelude to the {{ill|Battle of Shizugatake|ja|賤ヶ岳の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1603]] {{ill|April 14|ja|4月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Nihonbashi|ja|日本橋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in Chūō, Tokyo, was opened. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1642]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|徳川幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} established the office of {{ill|Kanjō Bugyō|ja|勘定奉行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1854]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate and U.S. envoy Perry signed the {{ill|Nippon-America Treaty|ja|日米和親条約|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (also known as the Kanagawa Treaty) in Yokohama, effectively ending national seclusion. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1860]] {{ill|March 24|ja|3月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – During the [[Sakuradamon Incident|桜田門外の変]], Tairō {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was attacked and killed by rōnin (including Mito rōnin) outside Sakurada Gate of Edo Castle. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Higashiyama Road Vanguard Government executed officials, including those of the [[Akahōtai|赤報隊]], as pseudo-officials.
