* [[Keichō]] 4th year (leap March) ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1599]] {{ill|April 27|ja|4月27日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Maeda Toshiie|ja|前田利家|qq=|12=draft}}, a military commander and one of the Tairō; he was the first lord of the Kaga Domain (born [[1538]]).
* 安政7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} 1860 [[March 24|ja|3月24日]]) – {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|qq=|12=draft}}, Tairō of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1815]]).
