== Events == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1583]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 24|qq=}}) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|羽柴秀吉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=}} (later known as {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=}}) captured {{ill|Kashida Katsuie|ja|柴田勝家|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kashida Katsuie|qq=}}’s forces by taking {{ill|Ise Province|ja|伊勢|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ise Province|qq=}}’s {{ill|Kameyama Castle|ja|亀山城 (伊勢国)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kameyama Castle|qq=}} in a prelude to the {{ill|Battle of Shizugatake|ja|賤ヶ岳の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Shizugatake|qq=}}. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1603]] {{ill|April 14|ja|4月14日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 14|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Nihonbashi|ja|日本橋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nihonbashi|qq=}} in Chūō, Tokyo, was opened. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1642]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 2|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|徳川幕府|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa shogunate|qq=}} established the office of {{ill|Kanjō Bugyō|ja|勘定奉行|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanjō Bugyō|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1854]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 31|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate and U.S. envoy Perry signed the {{ill|Nippon-America Treaty|ja|日米和親条約|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nippon-America Treaty|qq=}} (also known as the Kanagawa Treaty) in Yokohama, effectively ending national seclusion. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1860]] {{ill|March 24|ja|3月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 24|qq=}}) – During the [[Sakuradamon Incident|桜田門外の変]], Tairō {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naosuke|qq=}} was attacked and killed by rōnin (including Mito rōnin) outside Sakurada Gate of Edo Castle. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1868]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 26|qq=}}) – The Higashiyama Road Vanguard Government executed officials, including those of the [[Akahōtai|赤報隊]], as pseudo-officials.
== Births == * [[Shōō (Kamakura period)|Shōō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1288]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Later Fushimi Tennō|ja|後伏見天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Later Fushimi Tennō|qq=}}, the 93rd Emperor of Japan (died [[1336]]). * [[Tenbun]] 18th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1549]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 31|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tsuchi no Junkei|ja|筒井順慶|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchi no Junkei|qq=}}, a Sengoku daimyō (died [[1584]]). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannen|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1749]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōta Nan-Ō|ja|大田南畝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōta Nan-Ō|qq=}}, a playwright (died [[1823]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1825]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 20|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shiranui Kōuenemon|ja|不知火光右ヱ門|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiranui Kōuenemon|qq=}}, the 11th Yokozuna (died [[1879]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1832]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Matsunomon Sansōko|ja|松の門三艸子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsunomon Sansōko|qq=}}, a waka poet and geisha (died [[1914]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1849]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 26|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hirata Tōsuke|ja|平田東助|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirata Tōsuke|qq=}}, a bureaucrat and politician (died [[1925]]). * 嘉永4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1851]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 4|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ogino Ginko|ja|荻野吟子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ogino Ginko|qq=}}, a feminist and Japan’s first female doctor (died [[1913]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1855]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sugiura Shigetake|ja|杉浦重剛|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sugiura Shigetake|qq=}}, a thinker and educator (died [[1924]]). * 安政6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1859]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yasui Rimin|ja|安井理民|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasui Rimin|qq=}}, the founder of the first iteration of the Sōbu Railway (died [[1894]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1872]] {{ill|April 10|ja|4月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Itaya Hazan|ja|板谷波山|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itaya Hazan|qq=}}, a ceramic artist (died [[1963]]).
== Deaths == * [[Tenbun]] 20th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1551]] {{ill|April 8|ja|4月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 8|qq=}}) – {{ill|Oda Nobuhide|ja|織田信秀|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobuhide|qq=}}, a military commander and father of Oda Nobunaga (born [[1510]]). * [[Keichō]] 4th year (leap March) ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1599]] {{ill|April 27|ja|4月27日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 27|qq=}}) – {{ill|Maeda Toshiie|ja|前田利家|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maeda Toshiie|qq=}}, a military commander and one of the Tairō; he was the first lord of the Kaga Domain (born [[1538]]). * 安政7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1860 [[March 24|ja|3月24日]]) – {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naosuke|qq=}}, Tairō of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1815]]). * 慶応4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1868 [[March 26|ja|3月26日]]) – {{ill|Sagara Sōzō|ja|相楽総三|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sagara Sōzō|qq=}}, a proponent of Sonnō jōi (born [[1839]]).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|Shōmiji|ja|上巳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōmiji|qq=}} and {{ill|Hina Matsuri|ja|雛祭り|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hina Matsuri|qq=}} * {{ill|Hama-ori|ja|浜下り|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hama-ori|qq=}} – In Okinawa, women purify themselves by presenting food in tiered boxes at the beach; this tradition is combined with clam digging. * 玄天上帝誕辰 – The birthday celebration of the Taoist deity {{ill|Xuantian Shangdi|ja|玄天上帝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xuantian Shangdi|qq=}}. * サームニエッショーサーム – A traditional event of the Zhuang people in China (in their language: samnyiedcosam) celebrating ancestral veneration with large-scale singing gatherings, also known as "三月初三." * An independent New Year celebration by the Khor Lao ethnic group in Vietnam.
